  ],
  "remarks": "LLC “Urban Air Mobility Operations Center” (LLC UAMOC) is Russia-based company involved in the manufacturing of first-person view (FPV) unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs) for the Russian Armed Forces. The company was founded after the start of Russia’s full-scale war against Ukraine and rapidly expanded its production. LLC UAMOC produces FPV UAVs “Kort”, “Brus-1”, “Osa” and “Boomerang”, which are used in the war against Ukraine. It also launched a production and testing facility in illegally occupied Luhansk.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}